{"TopicId":201466,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal stuck on EVA facing one direction","CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-05T02:57:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-05T02:57:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I was trying to secure\u00A0a space station module with struts, so I went on EVA, and the Kerbal is stuck facing one direction.\u00A0What should I do?\u00A0 Note: I have tried changing the camera modes, it didn\u0027t \u00A0work\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zo68QtJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002274.25\u0022 height=\u0022669\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/zo68QtJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-05T06:00:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn your screenshot, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E is disabled. Turn it on and you should get full control again \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-05T20:10:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223949244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201466\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221617602446\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187982\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00224x4cheesecake\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, 4x4cheesecake said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn your screenshot, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E is disabled. Turn it on and you should get full control again\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat fixed it thanks!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}